OL,4,CFBI hate crime reports spike to 12-year
OL,5,Chigh in 2020
OL,6, US hate crimes hit a 12-year high in
OL,7, 2020, with over 10,000 people reporting
OL,8, offences related to their race, gender,
OL,9, sexuality, religion or disability.
OL,11,FAn annual FBI report released on Monday
OL,12,Ffound the number of reported crimes
OL,13,Fagainst Asian and black Americans in
OL,14,Fparticular surged last year.
OL,16,FReports were up 70% and 40% among both
OL,17,Fgroups, respectively, with black people
OL,18,Fbeing the most targeted group overall.
OL,20,FHate crimes have increased in the US
OL,21,Falmost ever year since 2014.
